name: Lafayette College
ACCREDAGENCY: Middle States Commission on Higher Education

lilgrant_international.Scholarship's Information: The Marquis Fellowship is a full-tuition award, and the Marquis Scholarship is a half-tuition award. Both are renewable for up to eight semesters, provided the student maintains a 3.00 GPA. Selection is based on the academic record and personal qualities that honor the Marquis de Lafayette. No separate application required; all applicants are automatically considered upon admission. An interview is encouraged.
